<p>Welcome to the official homepage of the Church of Infinite Simulations. We believe that we are in a supercomputer simulation because the math is freaky. All people are welcome here, including Agnostic and Atheist people.</p>

<h2 id="how-to-contribute">How to Contribute</h2>

